p: 20 mg PF and SPF extract were dissolved in 50% methanol solution (50:50, methanol-water, v/v), respectively. The solutions were ultrasonically processed (for 10 min), moderately diluted and centrifuged at 20,000 × g for 10 min. Then, 2 μL of the supernatants were injected into UPLC-Q-TOF/MS for analysis. Detailed methodological content can be found in the Supplementary Information.
